04:11.794 --> 04:13.338
Oh.

04:13.504 --> 04:15.048
How about I talk to them, hmm?

04:16.215 --> 04:18.259
I'll tell them...

04:20.678 --> 04:22.764
...you seem better to me.

04:24.682 --> 04:25.850
