04:27.769 --> 04:29.228
Sorry.

04:30.939 --> 04:32.440
Time for your meds.

04:40.448 --> 04:43.409
Something new needs to happen soon.

05:32.625 --> 05:34.627
It's just spit, right?

05:34.794 --> 05:36.295
Human spit.

05:39.298 --> 05:41.259
