you think you saw me getting out of a car?

43:36.573 --> 43:38.909
You don't have to be a dick about it.
It was you.

43:39.493 --> 43:40.744
Hey, no. You're wrong.

43:40.911 --> 43:44.623
In fact, that is one of the things
that we-- That I need to know.

43:44.790 --> 43:47.126
Who were the people
at the hospital that day?

43:47.293 --> 43:49.795
No. No, no, no. You're lying.

43:49.962 --> 43:53.173
- You're trying to confuse me, and-- No.
- David. David.

43:53.340 --> 43:54.466
No.

43:56.260 --> 43:58.804
David.

44:01.515 --> 44:03.559
David.

44:04.476 --> 44:06.520
Just take a deep breath.

44:06.687 --> 44:07.938
Try to be calm.

44:08.105 --> 44:10.858
Just try to relax, David.

44:21.910 --> 44:23.996
The gas, now.

44:24.163 --> 44:26.248
Use the gas.

44:26.415 --> 44:27.458
Use the gas.

