<i>She does.</i>

46:06.723 --> 46:08.434
<i>My boy.</i>

46:13.981 --> 46:15.732
<i>David.</i>

46:18.527 --> 46:20.821
<i>David, where are you?</i>

47:08.327 --> 47:09.703
Trick or treat.

47:09.870 --> 47:11.413
So exciting.

47:11.580 --> 47:13.207
