47:37.940 --> 47:40.442
What are you supposed to be?

47:43.445 --> 47:46.406
- Trick or treat.
- Trick or treat.

47:49.826 --> 47:51.119
Hi.

47:51.620 --> 47:53.413
Hi.

47:54.206 --> 47:56.416
They sent me home. And then I realized--

47:56.583 --> 47:58.877
I mean, the apartment's gone.

47:59.586 --> 48:01.213
So....

48:03.715 --> 48:05.842
Just for a few days?

48:11.348 --> 48:12.766
Of course.

48:12.933 --> 48:15.978
Uh, I'll talk to Ben.

48:16.311 --> 48:17.521
Come in. Come in.

48:19.773 --> 48:22.776
Avast, I've got Snapjacks
and red Krusteaz.

48:22.943 --> 48:26.488
Har! Har....

48:27.531 --> 48:29.283
- Holy shit.
- Ben.

48:29.449 --> 48:31.994
