48:50.679 --> 48:51.680
Uh....

48:51.847 --> 48:53.432
Another one?

48:54.391 --> 48:56.059
Here you go.

49:10.198 --> 49:12.951
- Heh.
- Is this...?

49:14.578 --> 49:16.371
Will this be okay?

49:17.456 --> 49:19.541
Yeah. I mean, this is....

49:20.000 --> 49:21.668
This is great.

49:22.210 --> 49:27.049
Uh, so, you know, Ben works early.

49:27.215 --> 49:30.052
