49:30.218 --> 49:34.181
So, um, you know, make yourself at home.

49:34.348 --> 49:36.600
Don't answer the phone.

49:39.478 --> 49:40.979
Okay.

49:45.859 --> 49:47.069
It's good.

49:47.235 --> 49:48.654
It's gonna be good.

49:50.447 --> 49:51.490
Okay?

49:51.657 --> 49:53.116
Yeah.

50:23.939 --> 50:25.565
