52:13.340 --> 52:15.509
Ah, no.

52:15.675 --> 52:17.552
- David?
- Mm-hmm?

52:17.761 --> 52:19.221
Yeah.

52:20.680 --> 52:22.224
- Are you okay?
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

52:22.390 --> 52:25.644
