52:25.811 --> 52:27.229
- Um....
- Oh.

52:27.395 --> 52:28.730
Sorry.

52:28.897 --> 52:30.398
No. It's, um--

52:31.441 --> 52:33.151
It's okay.

52:36.154 --> 52:38.782
It's just-- You know, Ben.

52:38.949 --> 52:41.618
