<i>David.</i>

53:08.228 --> 53:09.980
<i>David.</i>

53:17.195 --> 53:18.321
<i>They're coming and--</i>

53:19.447 --> 53:21.116
<i>And then they're gonna kill you.</i>

53:42.178 --> 53:43.889
<i>David.</i>

53:53.523 --> 53:55.525
<i>David.</i>

54:00.655 --> 54:02.324
<i>David.</i>

54:04.159 --> 54:05.744
Wake up.

54:14.336 --> 54:15.921
David.

54:17.297 --> 54:19.049
Over here.

54:20.091 --> 54:21.426
Let's stop pretending, huh?

54:21.718 --> 54:24.179
