57:51.469 --> 57:54.305
- I'm not really here.
- What do you mean?

57:54.472 --> 57:56.808
- Where else would you be?
- This is your memory...

57:56.975 --> 58:00.228
...of the day you called the hospital,
not the actual day.

58:00.395 --> 58:02.480
I'm inside your memory.

58:02.647 --> 58:03.982
Heh, but that's not--

58:06.860 --> 58:11.447
- I've been projected into your memory.
- I've been looking. No one would tell me.

58:11.614 --> 58:13.783
Syd, I don't understand. I was you--

58:13.950 --> 58:15.994
David, stop. I'm not really here.

58:17.579 --> 58:19.581
What do you mean?
Where else would you be?

58:19.747 --> 58:23.376
This is your memory
of the day you called the hospital.

58:24.085 --> 58:26.171
I've been projected into your memory.

58:26.337 --> 58:29.257
We're not on the street, not really.
