58:42.312 --> 58:44.022
You're in a government facility.

58:44.189 --> 58:47.150
- What are we--?
- You'll go for a swim. And I'll get you out.

58:47.317 --> 58:49.444
- A swim?
- Slowly, so they don't notice...

58:49.611 --> 58:51.696
...slide out of your chair
and into the water.

58:51.863 --> 58:54.782
And when you see the lights,
don't come up until you see me.

58:54.949 --> 58:56.743
David?

59:15.094 --> 59:17.347
There was a van.

59:17.513 --> 59:19.390
Yes. That was us.

59:19.557 --> 59:22.268
Who were the other two people?
The people who chased you?

59:22.435 --> 59:24.562
The ones who came to the hospital?

59:26.689 --> 59:30.109
David, are you with me?

59:32.445 --> 59:34.030
Yes.

59:37.367 --> 59:39.285
I'm here.

59:48.419 --> 59:50.588
It wasn't you...

59:50.838 --> 59:52.799
...at the hospital.

59:53.591 --> 59:55.843
Yeah. I told you.

59:56.511 --> 59:58.471
It wasn't you.

1:00:01.266 --> 1:00:05.478
<i>Slide out of your chair
and into the water, slowly.</i>

1:00:13.152 --> 1:00:14.696
Watch him.

1:00:14.862 --> 1:00:17.740
