do not make me press this button.

1:00:37.760 --> 1:00:39.053
Who are you people?

1:00:39.220 --> 1:00:42.473
No. I ask the questions.

1:00:47.770 --> 1:00:49.272
The girl.

1:00:49.439 --> 1:00:51.816
Where is the girl?

1:00:54.110 --> 1:00:55.903
I think you're about to find out.

1:01:02.910 --> 1:01:04.120
Do it now!

1:01:28.561 --> 1:01:29.771
Hi.

1:01:42.825 --> 1:01:44.660
Hi.

1:01:50.333 --> 1:01:51.793
David, don't.

1:01:51.959 --> 1:01:54.754
- I'm sorry. You can't touch my skin.
- Yes.

1:01:56.297 --> 1:01:57.715
This is Ptonomy.

1:01:59.133 --> 1:02:01.552
- And that's Kerry.
- Hey.

1:02:01.719 --> 1:02:03.346
Oh, hey.

1:02:04.263 --> 1:02:05.723
Hi.

1:02:05.890 --> 1:02:08.726
- Sorry about before.
- It's cool.

1:02:08.893 --> 1:02:11.938
- We like chasing after people.
- No. We like catching people.

1:02:12.105 --> 1:02:13.940
- Syd.
- We gotta go.

1:02:14.107 --> 1:02:15.691
Melanie's waiting.

1:02:16.984 --> 1:02:18.194
Who?

1:02:26.077 --> 1:02:30.540
Come on! Let's go, go, go!

1:02:34.293 --> 1:02:38.673
- Move, move, move!
- Fall back! Fall back!

1:02:40.842 --> 1:02:43.010
Keep moving!

1:02:52.562 --> 1:02:55.022
Move! Go, go, go!

1:03:08.703 --> 1:03:10.246
Go, this way.

1:03:10.413 --> 1:03:11.914
Go.

1:03:14.876 --> 1:03:16.836
Come on.

1:03:37.607 --> 1:03:40.109
- Syd, this is-- Wait.
- We can't stop. They're coming.

1:03:40.276 --> 1:03:42.028
I need you to stop. Please, Sydney.

1:03:42.195 --> 1:03:44.572
I have to know.

1:03:45.198 --> 1:03:46.282
Is--?

1:03:46.449 --> 1:03:47.950
Is this--?

1:03:48.367 --> 1:03:52.205
Is this real? I mean,
what if we're back at the hospital?

1:03:52.371 --> 1:03:54.665
What if none of this ever happened,
and we're--?

1:03:54.832 --> 1:03:57.960
Please, I have to know.

1:03:58.503 --> 1:04:00.713
Are you real?

1:04:01.839 --> 1:04:03.549
I'm real.

1:04:04.926 --> 1:04:06.636
This is real.

1:04:06.802 --> 1:04:08.387
Okay?

1:04:09.263 --> 1:04:11.057
I'm here.

1:04:11.724 --> 1:04:14.477
I came back for you. I love you.

1:04:16.479 --> 1:04:18.064
Okay?

1:04:18.231 --> 1:04:19.899
Okay.

1:04:23.486 --> 1:04:26.489
- You gonna say it too?
- I love you.

1:04:27.198 --> 1:04:29.075
We gotta go.

1:04:33.454 --> 1:04:35.289
Ms. Bird.

1:04:35.665 --> 1:04:37.792
This is David.

1:04:40.461 --> 1:04:42.338
Come on, son.

1:04:46.551 --> 1:04:47.927
Take my hand.
